Pass by value:
pass by refrence:
pass by address:

1) pass by value:
->fuction parameter we are passing only object it will not affect orignal value

2) pass by refrence:
->we are passing refrence of object so, whenever we apply chang it affect orignal value

3) pass by address:
->here, we are pass address of object so whenever apply changes in address it affect orignal value
